"Use this page to walk through the assessment import flow, from loading the "
"JSON file to selecting organisation units and confirming the assessment is "
"ready for capture."
msgstr ""
"Use this page to walk through the assessment import flow, from loading the "
"JSON file to selecting organisation units and confirming the assessment is "
"ready for capture."

