"Open Data Capture and select the assessment card you want to work with. The "
"list only shows active assessment tools that are already available in the "
"app."
msgstr ""
"Open Data Capture and select the assessment card you want to work with. The "
"list only shows active assessment tools that are already available in the "
"app."

