"Use the Report date step to enter the date for the assessment. You must "
"complete this step before moving into the form sections."
msgstr ""
"Use the Report date step to enter the date for the assessment. You must "
"complete this step before moving into the form sections."

msgid "The report date is stored as `occurredAt` in the event payload."
msgstr "The report date is stored as `occurredAt` in the event payload."

msgid "If the date field is blank or invalid, the form will not let you continue."
msgstr "If the date field is blank or invalid, the form will not let you continue."

