"report date."
msgstr ""
"Use Save progress to keep an unfinished record. Drafts are grouped by user "
"and program, and each saved draft stays unique by organisation unit and "
"report date."

msgid "Open the Drafts tab to continue saved work."
msgstr "Open the Drafts tab to continue saved work."

msgid ""
"Parent organisation units can show drafts from all descendants in the event "
"list."
msgstr ""
"Parent organisation units can show drafts from all descendants in the event "
"list."

msgid "Review submitted events"
msgstr "Review submitted events"

